author: Longfei Luan
text:
I just wanted to take a moment to say a huge thank you to my amazing gym family. I was honestly so touched and surprised by the lovely gift and the thoughtful supplements you gave me. It truly made my day and filled my heart with gratitude. üíñ

It‚Äôs not just about the gift itself ‚Äî it‚Äôs the kindness, love, and thought behind it that means the most to me. Knowing that you thought of me really touched my heart. I feel so lucky to be part of such a supportive and caring community where everyone encourages and uplifts one another.

Thank you for always making me feel appreciated and valued. Your gesture reminded me why I love being a part of this place ‚Äî it‚Äôs not just a gym, it‚Äôs a family. I‚Äôm deeply grateful for each one of you and the positive energy you bring into my fitness journey.

With lots of love and appreciation,
üí™‚ù§Ô∏è

author: Jeremy Lim
text: This is actually a huge anytime fitness branch. Counted about 3 squat racks and 3 platforms total with tons of free dumbbell weights. Sufficient toilets and water coolers as well.

author: Yu Kee Lim
text:
Maintenance can be an issue. One of the aircon units breaks down regularly. But for a few days now quite a number of them are down, making the place very warm and stuffy. Unfortunately it doesn‚Äôt seem that repairs would be done any time soon. Going to other gyms for now until they are fixed.

Edit: Appreciate the owner‚Äôs reply below but what would be more assuring would be clarity on timeline. This is similar to when the gym suddenly closed without prior notice for apparently urgent repairs. No update on what‚Äôs happening and members left hanging.

Honestly the staff there are very friendly but honestly the management leaves much to be desired.

author: Robin Ong
text:
Despite its non-linear layout, it contains lots of equipment (not visible at first glance due to its many walls and pillars).

I subtly like this characteristic, as it allows a workout without much distraction, iygiygi.

The outlet is larger than what I expected, has a wide range of equipment & its well kept.

text: The gym is nice with 3 squat racks and 2 platforms. They have also added new things like rogue olympic bar, trap bar, Swiss bar. Equipment is well maintained. Service is great where they greet you when you enter/leave. There are 4 showers but the lockers are rather small. The only thing i would have wanted is to have maybe 1 more bench in the functional training room. Many variety of cardio machine like treadmill, stair climber, cycle exercise bike, elliptical and rowing machine.

text:
Hi AF, good day to you.

I am writing to share my experience at this gym. Gym is well maintained and clean, spacious as well. I did not bring my key fob but counter staff was nice with verifying me. I was working out at the bench and needed weights from another occupied rack. The AF staff was watching his ‚Äúfriend‚Äù workout on it and I asked if I could take the weight. I tapped him and he turned to me after 2 seconds with a very annoyed look as if I owed him something. And said of course you can take why not with a rude tone. It‚Äôs a pinoy guy with red shoes. He did help me with working out harder lol. I would advise you to watch your attitude as a AF staff. This is my first and last time at this gym.

author: K Daron
text:
Good gym to deadlift in but bad for squats

Barbells include 2 rogue barbell and 2 ziva barbell. However, only one barbell has centre knurling and the other 3 doesnt.

Plates are hammer strength bumper and regular anytime fitness plates. Hammer strength bumper plates are extra bouncy so do take note.

Dumbbells range from 1-55kg+? However, the fixed barbell ranges only from 10-20kg but they do have the w-grip barbell that you can add plates on.

Machine selection is adequate. Basic machines are available. 2 cable machine

The gym is rather long and deep.

Free weights area has lots of mirror but lights are pretty dim

Downside is that the changing room mirror is terribly small but has one of the best lightings.

Overall good gym but it can get quite crowded at times and quite cold too so warmup well before training.

You cannot help take videos or pictures if your friend needs help with that. You get accused of conducting PT services on their premises. text:

Clean 5
Space 5
Machine Variation 3(Life Fitness)
Free weight 5 racks
Staff 3

Good for free weight, Back

The machines are new and the shower room is clean.
There are few machines and it is suitable for free wet.
It's difficult to train on weekends because there are so many people.
